data.description: Welcome to your charming oasis nestled in the heart of a serene neighborhood! This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom bungalow boasts a cozy ambiance and thoughtful touches throughout.  Step into the inviting living space, adorned with a stunning fireplace that serves as the focal point, perfect for gathering around on chilly evenings. Natural light floods the room, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that welcomes you home.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample storage, and plenty of counter space for meal preparation. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a quaint dining area, ideal for enjoying home-cooked meals with loved ones.  Venture downstairs to discover the bonus rooms in the basement, offering endless possibilities for customization. Whether you envision a home office, a playroom, or a cozy den, these versatile spaces await your personal touch.  Outside, the property beckons with its lush landscaping and a private backyard oasis, perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply unwinding amidst nature's beauty.  Conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and dining options, this bungalow offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this your forever home! Schedule a showing today and experience the magic for yourself.
